reviews.review_text:
not too fast and not too slow... another swell 73 performance 

another wicked eyes
Slammin' show I just saw Dark Star preform it in Louisville and I and to download it right away. Thank you archive!

A dime for a cup of coffee? Not a bad recording, some funny audio stuff here and there, Billy's mix is poor, they fiddle with it on Wharf Rat.

If you like THE DEAD in 73, this one will work.

El Paso is a total audience recording. They didn't turn the stage mics on...Oops!

Eat, drink be merry and listen to THE GRATEFUL DEAD.

3 Stars, for recording and performance.
